      <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-10 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
        <section id="install">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Instalação</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Instale globalmente via npm:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4">npm install -g xanascript</pre>
          <p class="mb-3">Verifique a instalação:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4">xs --help</pre>
          <p>Você deve ver uma lista de todos os comandos disponíveis.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="hello-world">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Hello World</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Crie um arquivo chamado <code>hello.xs</code>:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-3"><span class="text-gray-400">// hello.xs</span>
<span class="text-gray-400">// Hello World em XanaScript</span>
<span class="kw">PARTIU</span>()
<span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="str">"Hello, World!"</span>)
<span class="kw">ACABOU</span>()</pre>
          <p class="mb-3">Execute:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4">xs run hello.xs</pre>
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm text-green-700">
            <strong>Saída:</strong> <code>Hello, World!</code>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="cli-usage">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Uso da CLI</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">O XanaScript oferece uma CLI completa com comandos para executar, compilar, testar e empacotar:</p>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-4">
            <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 rounded-xl">
              <thead><tr><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Comando</th><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Descrição</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs run file.xs</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Executa um script (interpretador AST)</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs vm file.xs</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Executa via VM de bytecode</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs build file.xs</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Compila para JavaScript</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs build --opt file.xs</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Compila com otimização total</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs build --wasm file.xs</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Compila para binário WebAssembly</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs build --standalone file.xs</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Gera arquivo .js autocontido</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs test [dir]</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Executa arquivos de teste (*test*.xs)</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs fmt file.xs</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Formata o código-fonte</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs check file.xs</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Apenas verifica sintaxe</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs repl</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Inicia o REPL interativo</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs dev [file]</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Modo observação com hot reload</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs lsp</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Inicia servidor LSP (stdin/stdout)</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs init [dir]</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Gera a estrutura de um novo projeto</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs install [pkg]</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Instala um pacote</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs publish</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Publica no registro</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs search &lt;term&gt;</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Pesquisa pacotes</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs login</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Autentica no registro</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs whoami</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Mostra o usuário atual</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs logout</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Desconecta do registro</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs docs [src] [out]</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Gera documentação HTML</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>xs bench</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Executa benchmarks de desempenho</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="variables">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Variáveis</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Use <code>CRIA</code> para declarar variáveis. Os tipos são inferidos a partir do valor:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="kw">CRIA</span> nome = <span class="str">"XanaScript"</span>
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> ano = <span class="num">2026</span>
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> ativo = <span class="at">VERDADEIRO</span>
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> nada = <span class="at">NULO</span>
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> nums = [<span class="num">1</span>, <span class="num">2</span>, <span class="num">3</span>]
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> config = { nome: <span class="str">"server"</span>, porta: <span class="num">3000</span> }</pre>
          <p>Reatribua usando <code>=</code>:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto">nome = <span class="str">"XS"</span></pre>
        </section>

        <section id="types">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Tipos</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">XanaScript é dinamicamente tipado com os seguintes primitivos:</p>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-4">
            <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 rounded-xl">
              <thead><tr><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Tipo</th><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Exemplo</th><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Observações</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>NUMERO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>42</code>, <code>3.14</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Double IEEE 754 (Number do JS)</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>TEXTO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>"hello"</code>, <code>`template ${x}`</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Template strings com crases</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>BOOLEANO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>VERDADEIRO</code>, <code>FALSO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Literais booleanos em português</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>NULO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>NULO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Valor nulo</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>Array</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>[1, 2, 3]</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Arrays dinâmicos, tipos mistos permitidos</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>Object</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>{ a: 1 }</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Pares chave-valor</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>FUNCAO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>(x) => x * 2</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Funções de primeira classe</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="control-flow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Fluxo de Controle</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Condicionais usam palavras-chave em português:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="kw">SE LIGA SO</span> (x > <span class="num">10</span>) {
  <span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="str">"Greater than 10"</span>)
} <span class="kw">SENAO SE</span> (x > <span class="num">5</span>) {
  <span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="str">"Greater than 5"</span>)
} <span class="kw">SENAO</span> {
  <span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="str">"5 or less"</span>)
}</pre>
          <p class="mb-3">Laços:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="cm">// For loop</span>
<span class="kw">REPETE NA MORAL</span> (<span class="kw">CRIA</span> i = <span class="num">0</span>; i < <span class="num">5</span>; i += <span class="num">1</span>) {
  <span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(i)
}
<span class="cm">// While loop</span>
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> x = <span class="num">0</span>
<span class="kw">REPETE AI</span> (x < <span class="num">5</span>) {
  <span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(x)
  x += <span class="num">1</span>
}</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="functions">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Funções</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Funções nomeadas e anônimas:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="cm">// Named function</span>
<span class="kw">CHAMA ESSE CARA</span> soma(a, b) {
  <span class="kw">VOLTA</span> a + b
}
<span class="cm">// Arrow function</span>
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> dobro = (x) => x * <span class="num">2</span>
<span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="fn">soma</span>(<span class="num">3</span>, <span class="num">4</span>))
<span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="fn">dobro</span>(<span class="num">5</span>))</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="classes">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Classes & POO</h2>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="kw">CLASSE</span> Animal {
  <span class="kw">CONSTRUTOR</span>(nome) {
    <span class="kw">CRIA</span> <span class="kw">ISTO</span>.nome = nome
  }
  <span class="kw">METODO</span> falar() {
    <span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="kw">ISTO</span>.nome + <span class="str">" makes a sound"</span>)
  }
}
<span class="kw">CLASSE</span> Cachorro <span class="kw">HERDA</span> Animal {
  <span class="kw">METODO</span> falar() {
    <span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="kw">ISTO</span>.nome + <span class="str">" says: Woof!"</span>)
  }
}
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> rex = <span class="kw">NOVA</span> Cachorro(<span class="str">"Rex"</span>)
<span class="fn">rex.falar</span>()</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="pattern-matching">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Pattern Matching</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Use <code>COMBINA</code> para pattern matching expressivo com desestruturação:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="cm">// Match on value</span>
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> descrever = (val) => <span class="kw">COMBINA</span> (val) {
  <span class="kw">CASO</span> <span class="num">0</span> => <span class="str">"zero"</span>
  <span class="kw">CASO</span> <span class="num">1</span> => <span class="str">"one"</span>
  <span class="kw">CASO</span> _ => <span class="str">"many"</span>
}
<span class="cm">// Match on arrays with destructuring</span>
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> checkList = (items) => <span class="kw">COMBINA</span> (items) {
  <span class="kw">CASO</span> [] => <span class="str">"empty"</span>
  <span class="kw">CASO</span> [x] => <span class="str">"one item: "</span> + x
  <span class="kw">CASO</span> [x, y] => <span class="str">"two items"</span>
  <span class="kw">CASO</span> _ => <span class="str">"many items"</span>
}</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="async">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Async / Await</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Async/await nativo com <code>ASSINCRONO</code> e <code>ESPERA AI</code>:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="kw">CRIA</span> fetch = <span class="kw">ASSINCRONO</span> (url) => {
  <span class="kw">CRIA</span> res = <span class="kw">ESPERA AI</span> <span class="fn">AGORA VAI</span>(url)
  <span class="kw">CRIA</span> data = <span class="fn">PARSEIA</span>(res)
  <span class="kw">VOLTA</span> data
}
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> run = <span class="kw">ASSINCRONO</span> () => {
  <span class="kw">CRIA</span> users = <span class="kw">ESPERA AI</span> <span class="fn">fetch</span>(<span class="str">"https://api.example.com/users/1"</span>)
  <span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="str">"Name: "</span> + users.nome)
}
<span class="kw">ESPERA AI</span> <span class="fn">run</span>()</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="error-handling">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Tratamento de Erros</h2>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto"><span class="kw">TENTA</span> {
  <span class="kw">CRIA</span> data = <span class="fn">PARSEIA</span>(<span class="str">"{ invalid json }"</span>)
} <span class="kw">PEGA</span> (err) {
  <span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="str">"Error: "</span> + err)
}</pre>
        </section>

        <hr class="border-gray-200">

        <section id="orm" class="scroll-mt-24">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">ORM (TABELA)</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">XanaScript inclui um ORM nativo usando a palavra-chave <code>TABELA</code>. Defina um esquema e obtenha operações CRUD automáticas:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="kw">TABELA</span> Product {
  nome: <span class="typ">TEXTO</span>,
  preco: <span class="typ">NUMERO</span>,
  estoque: <span class="typ">NUMERO</span>
}
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> repo = Product
<span class="fn">repo.create</span>({ nome: <span class="str">"Keyboard"</span>, preco: <span class="num">250</span>, estoque: <span class="num">10</span> })
<span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="fn">repo.list</span>())
<span class="kw">CRIA</span> caros = <span class="fn">repo.findWhere</span>({ preco: { $gte: <span class="num">200</span> } })
<span class="fn">repo.update</span>(<span class="num">1</span>, { preco: <span class="num">200</span> })
<span class="fn">repo.delete</span>(<span class="num">2</span>)</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="macros">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Macros</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Geração de código em tempo de compilação com <code>MACRO</code>:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="kw">MACRO</span> <span class="fn">assert</span>(expr) {
  <span class="kw">CRIA</span> cond = expr[<span class="num">1</span>]
  <span class="kw">CRIA</span> code = <span class="fn">TEXTO</span>(cond)
  <span class="kw">VOLTA</span> [<span class="str">"SE LIGA SO (!"</span> + code + <span class="str">") { SOLTA O GRITO('Assertion failed: "</span> + code + <span class="str">"') }"</span>]
}
<span class="fn">assert</span>(x > <span class="num">0</span>)</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="wasm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">WebAssembly</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Compile XanaScript diretamente para binário WebAssembly:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4">xs build --wasm app.xs</pre>
        </section>

        <section id="http-server">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Servidor HTTP</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Servidor HTTP nativo com roteamento:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4"><span class="kw">CHAMA ESSE CARA</span> handler(req, res) {
  <span class="kw">SE LIGA SO</span> (req.url == <span class="str">"/"</span>) {
    <span class="fn">res.json</span>({ mensagem: <span class="str">"Hello from XanaScript!"</span> })
  } <span class="kw">SENAO</span> {
    <span class="fn">res.status</span>(<span class="num">404</span>).json({ erro: <span class="str">"Not found"</span> })
  }
}
<span class="kw">CRIA SERVIDOR</span>(<span class="num">3000</span>, handler)
<span class="kw">SOLTA O GRITO</span>(<span class="str">"Server running on :3000"</span>)</pre>
        </section>

        <hr class="border-gray-200">

        <section id="builtins">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Funções Nativas</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-4">
            <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 rounded-xl">
              <thead><tr><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Função</th><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Descrição</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>SOLTA O GRITO(x)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Imprime no console</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>AGORA VAI(url)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Requisição HTTP GET (assíncrono)</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>ESPERA AI(ms)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Pausa / delay (assíncrono)</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>SORTEIA(a, b)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Inteiro aleatório entre a e b</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>PARSEIA(json)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Interpreta string JSON</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>TAMANHO(x)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Tamanho de array ou string</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>TIPO(x)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Nome do tipo de um valor</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>OUVE_AQUI(k)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Lê variável de ambiente</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>OUVE_TUDO()</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Array de argumentos da CLI</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>CRIA SERVIDOR(p, h)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Inicia servidor HTTP na porta p</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>TEXTO(x)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Converte para string</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>NUMERO(x)</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Converte para número</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="keywords">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Palavras-chave</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-4">
            <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 rounded-xl">
              <thead><tr><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Palavra-chave</th><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Significado</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>CRIA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Declaração de variável</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>CHAMA ESSE CARA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Declaração de função</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>VOLTA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Retorna um valor</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>SE LIGA SO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Condicional if</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>SENAO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Else</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>REPETE NA MORAL</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Laço for</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>REPETE AI</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Laço while</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>VOA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Sai do laço (break)</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>CONTINUA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Continua para próxima iteração</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>SOLTA O GRITO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Saída no console</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>CLASSE</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Declaração de classe</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>HERDA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Extende (herança)</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>ISTO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Referência this</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>NOVA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Instancia uma classe</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>CONSTRUTOR</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Construtor da classe</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>METODO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Método da classe</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>TENTA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Bloco try</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>PEGA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Bloco catch</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>COMBINA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Pattern matching</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>CASO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Braço case no match</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>MACRO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Macro em tempo de compilação</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>TABELA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Declaração de tabela ORM</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>IMPORTA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Importa módulo</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>EXPORTA</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Exporta símbolo</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>PARTIU</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Ponto de entrada do programa</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>ACABOU</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Fim do programa</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>ASSINCRONO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Função assíncrona</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>VERDADEIRO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Booleano true</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>FALSO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Booleano false</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>NULO</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Valor nulo</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="errors">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Códigos de Erro</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-4">
            <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 rounded-xl">
              <thead><tr><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Código</th><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Significado</th><th class="text-left p-3 bg-gray-50 font-semibold">Causa</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>E001</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Token inesperado</td><td class="p-3 border-t">Erro de sintaxe</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>E002</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Variável não definida</td><td class="p-3 border-t">Referência a variável não declarada</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>E003</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Não é uma função</td><td class="p-3 border-t">Chamada de um valor que não é função</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>E004</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Tipo incompatível</td><td class="p-3 border-t">Incompatibilidade de tipos em operação</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>E005</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Sintaxe inválida</td><td class="p-3 border-t">Erro do parser</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>E006</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Divisão por zero</td><td class="p-3 border-t">Divisão ou módulo por zero em execução</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>E007</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Índice fora dos limites</td><td class="p-3 border-t">Índice do array além do comprimento</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>E100</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Falha HTTP</td><td class="p-3 border-t">Erro de rede no AGORA VAI()</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="p-3 border-t"><code>E999</code></td><td class="p-3 border-t">Erro interno</td><td class="p-3 border-t">Erro inesperado do compilador/runtime</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="lsp">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Protocolo LSP</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">XanaScript inclui uma implementação do Language Server Protocol para integração com IDEs:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-3">xs lsp</pre>
          <p>Funcionalidades: erros de sintaxe, autocomplete, informações ao passar o mouse, ir para definição, símbolos do documento. Compatível com VS Code, Neovim e qualquer cliente LSP.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="package-manager">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-3">Gerenciador de Pacotes</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">XanaScript possui um gerenciador de pacotes nativo com um registro público em <a href="https://xanascript.xyz/packages" class="text-pinky-400 hover:underline">xanascript.xyz/packages</a>:</p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm overflow-x-auto mb-4">xs login
xs search &lt;term&gt;
xs install &lt;package-name&gt;
xs publish</pre>
        </section>

